Overview

This dashboard shows Compass overview related to the SpyCloud Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested compass from SpyCloud.

It showcases the aggregate count of infected IP addresses, and infected email accounts. It presents the distribution of compass events across infected time. Furthermore, it highlights the top 10 infected users, top 10 hostnames by infected machine ID, and the top 10 compromised countries. By default, it retrieves new compass events every day.
